{"id": "sos003", "name": "Audio_Arc_682_06_06", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gate_Conner", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. Security guard"], "content": "Wolf-01, head back to the city!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "Engine stalls"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. Security guard"], "content": "Colin? Where is... everyone?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "... ugh...\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "Falls down"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. Security guard"], "content": "Wah!? Medic! Hurry up!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "Ugh...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "You're awake.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "You're... ogh!\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "Don't. Just lie down. This isn't a minor injury.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "......\nLuka... he's...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "... Sorry. We haven't received either his signal or his vital signs. We're going to send another squad to the mission location to confirm his condition.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "No... ! ... Ugh!!\nMy mission report...! You haven't seen it!?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "We saw it. Mr. Neumann, you'll be commended for your bravery in an appropriate manner. Let us handle the next move. We think you ought to rest for a while.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "What... what are you saying? I can still take on missions. I told you I wanted to go back and settle things with him myself...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "Mr. Neumann, listen. You've got to trust us. This is best for you.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "Riya... his wife, his child. They deserve to know the truth.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "We sorry, but according to the regulations, they don't. None of us are happy about the tragedy that occurred during this mission. \nProfessionals will deal with the losses that squad members and their families have suffered. They will get everything they need. \nAs for the details of the mission, we cannot let any of it leak to the outside world, even if it's family. You know that.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "... What kind of s*** rule is that? Do you know what happened to us!?\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "As I mentioned before, we've already collected and fully reviewed your mission report. We're very clear on what happened. However, this is Top Secret, highly confidential. It's not even going to be seen by members of the exploration team.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "What the hell... are you talking about... explain yourself... oof!\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "Your body needs to rest. The doctor's already given you a dose of meds. They'll be great for your recovery and allow you to recuperate in peace.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "No... let me... outta here... zzZ...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. Nurse"], "content": "Mr. Neumann, time to eat.\nMr. Neumann... ?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. Nurse"], "content": "......!\nMr. Neumann's gone!\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Doorbell_NEKO", "Doorbell"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Coming!\n......? Sir, who are you looking for?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "... Sagar? You've grown so much...\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "Sagar, who is it?\n... Colin...!? My god! Your wounds... what happened!?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "People from A.R.C.... have they come yet?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "Eh? No... what, what's wrong!?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "Oh, yea...? Haha...\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Mom...?\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "Sagar, go play in your room, okay?\nColin, you scared us half to death. What's going on?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "... I'm sorry... <i>*sob*... *sob*</i>... sorry... Luka...\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. Security guard"], "content": "Got you! Mr. Neumann! You can't keep running! You're coming with us!\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "Let... <font size=\"3.6\">Let me go!!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "What are you doing!? What on earth happened!? What's wrong with Luka!?\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "We're sorry, Mr. Neumann's psyche hasn't stabilized. I'll come by and explain everything.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "What are you saying...!? Let me go! Don't listen to them!\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "Mrs. Riya, I'm sorry to have to tell you...\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gate_Conner", "門が開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. セキュリティ"], "content": "Wolf-01帰還！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "エンジンが止まる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. セキュリティ"], "content": "Colinさん？他の……方々は……\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……ぅっ……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "倒れる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. セキュリティ"], "content": "うわあ！\n医療班！急いで！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "んん……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "目が覚めたか。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "あなたは……っく……！\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "構わん。横になったままでいい。\nひどいケガだ。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "………\nLuka……は……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "……残念だが、彼のシグナルもバイタルサインも途絶えたままだ。\n他の隊を現場へ送り状況確認をする予定だ。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "ダメです！……っ！\n我々の任務レポートを……！ご覧になってないんですか！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "見たさ。\nNeumann君、君の活躍は称賛に値する。\n今後のことについては、我々に任せなさい。\n君にはまだ休養が必要だろう。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "何を……おっしゃっているんです？\n私はまだ任務に出れます。\n約束したんです……落とし前を付けると……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "Neumann君。言うことを聞きなさい。\nこれは君にとっても一番いい選択だ。\n我々を信じるんだ。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "Riyaは……彼の奥さんと子供には……真相を知る権利があるはずです。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "残念だが、これは決まりだ。\n彼らにはその権利はない。\n今回の任務中に起きた悲しい事故を喜ぶ者はいない。\n隊員と遺族のことはこちらに任せなさい。君は何も心配しなくていい。\nだが、今回の任務の詳細について、我々は口外することはできない。\n例えそれが家族であってもだ。分かっているだろう？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……そんなバカげたルール……あなたに何が分かるんだ！\n何があったかも知らないくせに！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "先ほども言った通り、君のレポートは見せてもらった。\n何があったのかについては、よく理解しているつもりだ。\nだが、これは最高機密に値する。\n探査隊員であってもこの情報を知ることは許されない。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "さっきから……何を言っているんだ……納得できるように……ぐっ！\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "君にはまだ休息が必要だ。\n回復に効く薬を医者が投与してくれた。\nゆっくり休むといい。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "ダメだ……私を……ここから……zzZ……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 看護師"], "content": "Neumannさん、お食事ですよ。\nNeumannさん……？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 看護師"], "content": "……！\nNeumannさんがいません！\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Doorbell_NEKO", "ドアベル"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "はーい！\n……？おじさんだれ？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……Sagarか？大きくなったな……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "Sagar、どちら様？\n……Colinさん……！？まあまあ！\nひどいケガ……何があったんですか！\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "A.R.C.の人間は……来ましたか。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "え？\nいいえ……ど、どうしたんです！？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "そうですか……はは……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "母さん……？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "Sagar、先に部屋に戻ってなさい。ね？\nColinさん、本当にどうなさったんですか？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……すまない……っ……本当に申し訳ない……Lukaが……\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. セキュリティ"], "content": "見つけたぞ！\nNeumannさん！勝手に動き回られては困ります！\n帰りましょう！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "放せ……<font size=\"3.6\">放せ！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "何だっていうんですか！\n本当に何があったんです！？うちの人がどうしたんですか！？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "申し訳ございません。\n彼は現在精神が錯乱している状態でして……\n私が彼に代わってご説明します。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "なんだと！？……放せ！\nそいつの話を聞いてはいけない！\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "Riyaさん、とても悲しいことですが……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gate_Conner", "大門開啟"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 保全"], "content": "Wolf-01 返城！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "引擎熄火"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 保全"], "content": "Colin？其他……人呢？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……唔……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "倒下"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 保全"], "content": "哇！？醫護人員！快點！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "你醒了。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "你是……唔！\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "不用了，躺著就好。你的傷勢不輕。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……。\nLuka……呢……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "……很遺憾，他的訊號跟生命跡象都沒有再回傳，我們會派遣別的小隊再次前往任務地點確認狀況。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "不行！……唔！\n我的任務紀錄……！你們沒看嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "我們已經看過了。Neumann 先生，您英勇的表現會得到應有的表揚。接下來的行動就交給我們來安排吧，我們認為您需要休養一陣子。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "你在……說什麼？我還能出任務，我說過我要親自回去找他算帳……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "Neumann 先生，請聽令。相信我們吧，這對您是最好的安排。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "Riya……他老婆，還有小孩。他們有權知道真相。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "很遺憾，根據規定，他們沒有。\n此次任務中發生的悲劇我們大家都不樂見，會有專人處理隊員與他們的家人的損失，並讓他們得到應得的照顧。但對於任務的細節我們一概無法透漏給外部人士知道，即便是家屬，這點你清楚的。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……這算什麼狗屁規定？你知道我們遭遇到了什麼嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "我說過，我們已經回收並且完整閱覽您的任務紀錄了，我們很清楚。但此屬最高機密，甚至不會透漏給探勘隊的成員。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "你到底……在說什麼東西……給我好好解釋……唔！\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "您的身體尚須好好休息，醫生已經給您一定劑量的藥劑，對恢復會很有幫助，還請您好好靜養。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "不……放我……走……zzZ……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 護士"], "content": "Neumann 先生，用餐時間到囉。\nNeumann 先生……？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 護士"], "content": "……！\nNeumann 先生不見了！\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Doorbell_NEKO", "門鈴"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "來了！\n……？叔叔你找哪位？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……Sagar 嗎？長這麼大了……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "Sagar，是誰啊？\n……Colin……！？天啊！你的傷……發生什麼事！？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "A.R.C. 的人……還沒來過嗎？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "咦？沒有啊……怎、怎麼了！？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "是嗎……？哈哈……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "媽媽……？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "Sagar，你先回房間玩，好嗎？\nColin，你嚇到我們了，到底怎麼了？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……對不起……嗚嗚……對不起……Luka……\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 保全"], "content": "找到了！Neumann 先生！您還不能亂跑啊！\n請跟我們回去！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "放……<font size=\"3.6\">放開我！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "你們幹嘛！？到底發生什麼事了！？Luka 怎麼了！？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "很抱歉，Neumann 先生精神尚未穩定，接下來請由我來說明吧。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "你說什麼！？……放開我！別聽他說的！\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "Riya 小姐，很遺憾必須通知您……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gate_Conner", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 경비원"], "content": "Wolf-01은 귀환하라!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "엔진 가동"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 경비원"], "content": "Colin? 다른 사....람은?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "......으윽......\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "쓰러진다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 경비원"], "content": "아니! ? \n당장 의료진을 불러와! 빨리!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "윽......\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "깨어났군.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "당신은......큭! \n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "우선 누워 있도록.\n부상이 심각하니 말이야.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "......\nLuka......는......\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "......유감이네. 현재 위치 시그널과 바이탈 사인 모두 반응이 없는 상태야. 다른 소대를 파견해서 임무지의 상황을 확인할 계획이네.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "안 됩니다! ......윽! \n임무에서의 기록을.... 못 보신 겁니까?......!\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "이미 다 봤어.\nNeumann, 자네가 임무에서 보여준 용기와 그 용맹은 분명 모든 이의 모범이 되기에 충분하다네.  분명 자네에게 표창이 수여될 거야. 이제 그 임무는 우리들에게 맡기도록 해. 자네는 휴식이 필요한 것 같으니.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "지금......무슨 말을 하는 겁니까? 전 아직 임무를 수행할 수 있습니다. 돌아가서 무조건 제 손으로 이 빚을 갚아줘야만...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "Neumann, 명령일세. 우리들을 믿게. 자네에게도 이게 가장 좋은 결정이야.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "그 녀석에겐.... 아내 Riya와 자식이 있습니다. 가족들도 진실을 알아야만 할 권리가 있습니다.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "유감이지만 규정에 따르면 그 가족들에게 그럴 권한은 없네. 이번 임무에서 발생한 비극은 우리들도 모두 유감스럽게 생각하고 있어. 팀원들의 가족들에게 사람을 보내서 돈을 배상하고 그들을 잘 돌봐줄 걸세. 하지만 임무에 관한 상세한 내용은 외부인에게 발설할 수 없어. 설령 그게 가족이라도 말이야. 자네도 잘 알고 있지 않은가?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "......그게 무슨 x 같은 규정입니까? 당신은 우리가 무슨 일을 겪었는지 알기나 해!?\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "말했듯이, 우리 모두 자네가 기록한 것들을 모두 봤다네. 우리도 잘 알고 있어. 하지만 그건 최고 기밀 사항이야. 탐사대 일원에게도 공개할 수 없는 것이지.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "당신 도대체.....무슨 소릴 하고 있는 거야... 설명할 거면 똑바로 설.... 큭!\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "몸을 눕혀서 우선 안정을 취하도록 하게. 의사가 이미 일정량의 약을 투여했네. 어느 정도는 도움이 될 거야. 조용히 쉬고 있게나.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "안 돼......나를......보내....줘.....zzZ......\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 간호사"], "content": "Neumann 씨, 식사 시간입니다.\nNeumann 씨......? \n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 간호사"], "content": "......! \nNeumann 씨가 사라졌어요!\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Doorbell_NEKO", "도어벨"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "왔다! \n......? 아저씨, 누구 찾으러 오셨어요?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "......Sagar 맞니? 많이 컸구나......\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "Sagar, 누구 왔니? \n......Colin......!? 세상에! 이 상처는.... 대체 무슨 일이죠!?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "A.R.C.에서 보낸 사람이... 아직 안 왔습니까?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "네? 안 왔는데... 무, 무슨 일이죠!?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "그렇습니까......? 하하하......\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "엄마......? \n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "Sagar, 우선 방으로 들어가서 놀고 있으렴, 알았지? Colin 씨, 놀래키지 말고 제대로 설명해주세요.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "......죄송합니다......흐흑......죄송합니다......Luka가......\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 경비원"], "content": "찾았다! Neumann 씨! 이렇게 멋대로 행동하면 곤란합니다! 어서 우리와 함께 돌아가시죠!\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "놔......<font size=\"3.6\">이거 놓으라고!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "뭐하는 짓이에요!? 대체 무슨 일이죠!? Luka가 어떻게 됐길래!?\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "죄송합니다. Neumann의 정신 상태가 아직 불안정한 상황이라서. 나머지는 저희가 설명해드리도록 하죠.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "그게 뭔 소리야! ? ......이거 놔! 저 녀석이 하는 말 듣지 마세요!\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "Riya 씨, 유감이지만 당신께서 아셔야만 할 일이...\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gate_Conner", "大門開啟"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 保全"], "content": "Wolf-01 返城！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "引擎熄火"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 保全"], "content": "Colin？其他……人呢？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……唔……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "倒下"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 保全"], "content": "哇！？醫護人員！快點！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "你醒了。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "你是……唔！\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "不用了，躺著就好。你的傷勢不輕。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……。\nLuka……呢……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "……很遺憾，他的訊號跟生命跡象都沒有再回傳，我們會派遣別的小隊再次前往任務地點確認狀況。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": 