lin"], "content": "A.R.C. 的人……還沒來過嗎？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "咦？沒有啊……怎、怎麼了！？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "是嗎……？哈哈……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "媽媽……？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "Sagar，你先回房間玩，好嗎？\nColin，你嚇到我們了，到底怎麼了？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……對不起……嗚嗚……對不起……Luka……\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 保全"], "content": "找到了！Neumann 先生！您還不能亂跑啊！\n請跟我們回去！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "放……<font size=\"3.6\">放開我！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "你們幹嘛！？到底發生什麼事了！？Luka 怎麼了！？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "很抱歉，Neumann 先生精神尚未穩定，接下來請由我來說明吧。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "你說什麼！？……放開我！別聽他說的！\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "Riya 小姐，很遺憾必須通知您……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gate_Conner", "大门开启"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 保全"], "content": "Wolf-01 返城！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "引擎熄火"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 保全"], "content": "Colin？其他……人呢？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……唔……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "倒下"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 保全"], "content": "哇！ ？医护人员！快点！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切换讯号]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "你醒了。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "你是……唔！\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "不用了，躺着就好。你的伤势不轻。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……。\nLuka……呢……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "……很遗憾，他的讯号跟生命迹象都没有再回传，我们会派遣别的小队再次前往任务地点确认状况。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "不行！ ……唔！\n我的任务纪录……！你们没看吗！ ？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "我们已经看过了。 Neumann 先生，您英勇的表现会得到应有的表扬。接下来的行动就交给我们来安排吧，我们认为您需要休养一阵子。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "你在……说什么？我还能出任务，我说过我要亲自回去找他算帐……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "Neumann 先生，请听令。相信我们吧，这对您是最好的安排。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "Riya……他老婆，还有小孩。他们有权知道真相。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "很遗憾，根据规定，他们没有。\n此次任务中发生的悲剧我们大家都不乐见，会有专人处理队员与他们的家人的损失，并让他们得到应得的照顾。但对于任务的细节我们一概无法透漏给外部人士知道，即便是家属，这点你清楚的。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……这算什么狗屁规定？你知道我们遭遇到了什么吗！ ？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "我说过，我们已经回收并且完整阅览您的任务纪录了，我们很清楚。但此属最高机密，甚至不会透漏给探勘队的成员。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "你到底……在说什么东西……给我好好解释……唔！\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "您的身体尚须好好休息，医生已经给您一定剂量的药剂，对恢复会很有帮助，还请您好好静养。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "不……放我……走……zzZ……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 护士"], "content": "Neumann 先生，用餐时间到啰。\nNeumann 先生……？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 护士"], "content": "……！\nNeumann 先生不见了！\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切换讯号]</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Doorbell_NEKO", "门铃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "来了！\n……？叔叔你找哪位？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……Sagar 吗？长这么大了……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "Sagar，是谁啊？\n……Colin……！ ？天啊！你的伤……发生什么事！ ？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "A.R.C. 的人……还没来过吗？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "咦？没有啊……怎、怎么了！ ？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "是吗……？哈哈……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "妈妈……？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "Sagar，你先回房间玩，好吗？\nColin，你吓到我们了，到底怎么了？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "……对不起……呜呜……对不起……Luka……\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["A.R.C. 保全"], "content": "找到了！ Neumann 先生！您还不能乱跑啊！\n请跟我们回去！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "放……<font size=\"3.6\">放开我！ ！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Riya"], "content": "你们干嘛！ ？到底发生什么事了！ ？ Luka 怎么了！ ？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "很抱歉，Neumann 先生精神尚未稳定，接下来请由我来说明吧。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Colin"], "content": "你说什么！ ？ ……放开我！别听他说的！\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Leo"], "content": "Riya 小姐，很遗憾必须通知您……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}